trans-unit.source: Represents the collection of Response Headers as defined in RFC 2616.
This type is derived from <xref:System.Net.Http.Headers.HttpHeaders>.
trans-unit.target: Esse tipo é derivado de <xref:System.Net.Http.Headers.HttpHeaders>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the value of the <see langword="Accept-Ranges" /> header for an HTTP response.
The value of the <see langword="Accept-Ranges" /> header for an HTTP response.
trans-unit.target: O valor do cabeçalho <see langword="Accept-Ranges" /> para uma resposta HTTP.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates if the <see langword="Connection" /> header for an HTTP response contains Close.
